--- !u!114 &1712519149
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1712519147}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9a5add2d87d5add4b9c5688f8ab8a160, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  infoText: {fileID: 1001350856}
  prevButton: {fileID: 1171804867}
  nextButton: {fileID: 877924228}
  pages:
  - '                          1

    Welcome To Demogorgan Sweeper,

    click on
    any tile with your mouse''s left click or touchpad to reveal the truth hidden
    behind the tile, right click or click with 2 fingers on touchpad to mark a tile
    with a bomb,'
  - '                          2

    There are 25 demogorgans hidden in the field,
    clicking on a space with the demogorgan will cause you to lose, clicking on a
    safe tile will allow you to know any nearby(adjacent) demogorgans represented
    by the number on top of the tile,'
  - '                          3

    There can be a maximum of 8 demogorgan to a
    tile you might click, use your brain and mental abaility to scout and mark out
    all the 25demogorgans with the bombs, if all 25 demogorgans are marked successfully;'
  - '                          4

    BOOM!! all the demogorgans would be vanquished
    and you would win and complete the game and free to move on to the next level,

    in
    case of incorrect demgorgan guesses, nothing would happen really.'
  timerManager: {fileID: 840953015}
